願意為香港失業。你又願意犧牲幾多？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家醒下啦，如果運動輸咗，唔好問點解。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，決一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人，加油！</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"6.9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"6.12"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"6.16"},{"pid":"a14dc2b0429854844c1b48aab5dacd90b12ebed6","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd39936e63e19399f95a42b40439f50ef5454e5e","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee228c51ca93ab26384ea891a625bb3efde4a61","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3155c6ebe207212a07f62ac155b475d6f2a708b5","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"6.9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"6.12"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"6.16"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"7.1"},{"pid":"d30a3e024226353b8b9e7a00eabf598c0d8582a8","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14dc2b0429854844c1b48aab5dacd90b12ebed6","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd39936e63e19399f95a42b40439f50ef5454e5e","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee228c51ca93ab26384ea891a625bb3efde4a61","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"6.12"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"6.16"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"7.1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"7.14"},{"pid":"38b6da153ebf61dab130e3301b0b5d405bfb026c","tid":1538753,"uid":305577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30a3e024226353b8b